│ ensure that `Preheader` is not `nullptr` before proceeding with the transformation. If  │
│ `Preheader` is `nullptr`, the function should return early, as there is no valid        │
│ preheader to work with.                                                                 │
│                                                                                         │
│ Here is the proposed fix:                                                               │
│                                                                                         │
│ 1. Add a check after retrieving the `Preheader` to ensure it is not `nullptr`.          │
│ 2. If `Preheader` is `nullptr`, log a debug message (if applicable) and return early.   │
│                                                                                         │
